<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="544" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,419,1995]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,289,1895,1922]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Biology</emphasis>
. The preferred environments are alluvial localities in the mountain areas at altitudes from 
<quantity metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="0.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" unit="m" value="1400.0" valueMax="2000.0" valueMin="800.0">800 to 2000 m</quantity>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Stackelberg, A. A." box="[188,395,1931,1958]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="350 - 400" refId="ref11979" refString="Stackelberg, A. A. (1952) A new Syrphidae (Diptera) of Palaearctic fauna. Proceedings of Zoological Institute of Academy of Sciences of USSR, 12, 350 - 400. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1952">Stackelberg, 1952</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Stackelberg, A. A." box="[407,466,1931,1958]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="898 - 904" refId="ref12164" refString="Stackelberg, A. A. (1959) The Palaearctic species of the genus Chrysogaster Mg. (Diptera, Syrphidae). Entomologicheskoye obozreniye, 38 (4), 898 - 904. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1959">1959</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Peck, L. V." box="[479,608,1932,1959]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="94 - 127" refId="ref11224" refString="Peck, L. V. (1968) Materials on the syrphid flies (Diptera, Syrphidae) fauna of Kirghizia. In: Peck, L. V. (Chief Ed.), Entomological research in Kirghizia. Ilim, Frunze, pp. 94 - 127. [in Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1968">Peck, 1968</bibRefCitation>
). Adults fly in spring and summer (15.IV–26.VI). The flowers visited are 
<taxonomicName box="[151,247,1968,1994]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Berberidaceae" genus="Berberis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,247,1968,1994]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Berberis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. and Umbelliferae (
<bibRefCitation author="Peck, L. V." box="[503,633,1968,1995]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="94 - 127" refId="ref11224" refString="Peck, L. V. (1968) Materials on the syrphid flies (Diptera, Syrphidae) fauna of Kirghizia. In: Peck, L. V. (Chief Ed.), Entomological research in Kirghizia. Ilim, Frunze, pp. 94 - 127. [in Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1968">Peck, 1968</bibRefCitation>
). The larva is unknown.
</paragraph>
